<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tensers - Scan Results</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
      @tailwind base;
      @tailwind components;
      @tailwind utilities;
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto p-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mb-10">Scan Results</h1>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Header Analysis</h2>
          <p id="headerContent" class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Analyzing headers for potential phishing indicators...
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <button class="bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition">
              View Details
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Content Analysis</h2>
          <p id="emailContent" class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Evaluating content for suspicious phrases and links...
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <button class="bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition">
              View Details
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mt-6">
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold">Phishing Indicator:</div>
          <span id="phishingIndicator" class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-600">90%</span>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">High risk of phishing detected.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold">Confidence Score:</div>
          <span id="confidenceScore" class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-600">90%</span>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">High confidence in analysis accuracy.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Predictions</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-sm font-bold">Header Analysis:</div>
            <span id="headerAnalysis" class="text-lg font-semibold">90%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-sm font-bold">Content Analysis:</div>
            <span id="contentAnalysis" class="text-lg font-semibold">90%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Potential Threats Detected</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Suspicious URL: <span class="font-semibold text-red-600">http://malicious-site.com</span></li>
          <li>Embedded scripts detected that may compromise security.</li>
          <li>Unusual sender email address: <span class="font-semibold text-red-600">alert@phishing.com</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Recommended Actions</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Consider blocking the suspicious URL.</li>
          <li>Review the email sender's domain for legitimacy.</li>
          <li>Implement additional security measures for email filtering.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <button class="bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded hover:bg-blue-800 transition">
          Enhance Report
        </button>
        <button class="bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded hover:bg-gray-500 transition ml-4">
          Download Report
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">User Feedback</h3>
        <textarea class="w-full p-4 border border-gray-300 rounded mt-2" rows="4" placeholder="Share your thoughts on the scan results..."></textarea>
        <button class="bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition mt-2">
          Submit Feedback
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
